titles.title: Yes, My Spirit Is Stronger Than My Flesh

verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Yes, my spirit is stronger than my flesh.
Yes, my spirit is stronger than my flesh.
Time has come for flesh to die
I'll not listen to your cry
My spirit is stronger than my flesh.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Yes, my spirit is stronger than my flesh.
Yes, my spirit is stronger than my flesh.
Flesh you cannot rule in me
From your bondage I am free.
My spirit is stronger than my flesh.
